Rule 1 never follow ysac step by step

Sausage Balls
6 c Bisquick
2 lb extra-sharp Cheddar
1 lb sage sausage
1 lb hot sausage
Bring all ingredients to room temperature.  Shred cheese.  Mix all ingredients.  Form into 1" balls.  Bake 20 min on greased baking sheet at 300 F.

Bourbon Balls
12 oz vanilla wafers finely crushed
1 c chopped pecans
3/4 c powdered sugar
2 T cocoa powder
2-1/2 T light corn syrup
1/2 c borubon
Mix dry ingredients.  Add wet ingredients.  Roll into 1" balls.  Roll balls in powdered sugar.  Store in air tight container.
